data.description: A lovely, well-maintained, 4 bedroom Crooked Creek home with 2 car garage.  A short walk puts you into the Town Park and quaint, charming Banner Elk!  Everything you need on the main level, plus a full guest suite upstairs.  Over 900 square feet of deck space to enjoy the outdoors, including the beautiful trees and flowers in the back, side and front yards!  Flat paved roads to this home, providing great year round access.  The elevation of 3,700 feet will bring you relief from warm temperatures elsewhere.  Several new or newer appliances, luxury wood flooring throughout the main floor, and an encapsulated crawl space with new dehumidifier.  A great price for over 2,400 heated square feet and a two car garage.  Furnishings are negotiable.  With its Banner Elk location, skiing, hiking, the Blue Ridge Parkway, Grandfather Mountain, restaurants, shopping, Valle Crucis, Boone, Blowing Rock and much more are close by.
